Sol:
clc
close all
clear
x = linspace(-3,3,30);
y = linspace(-3,3,30);
n=length(x);
m=length(y);
f=zeros(n,m);
for i=1:n
for j=1:m
f(i,j) = (x(i)*y(j))/(x(i)*x(i));
end
end

ylabel('y')
zlabel('z')
colorbar
